{"tid":652552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子睦鄰街公廁上吊　繩斷墮地死亡","createTime":"2018-05-04T02:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T05:07:12.000Z","uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6d3b850300acf1c479db44dfb66b1efb16f77f0c","tid":652552,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T02:25:08.000Z","msg":"黃大仙睦鄰街遊樂場一個傷殘人士廁所，早上8時34分，清潔工進入該廁所內清潔時，發現一名30餘歲男子倒臥地上，陷入昏迷，救護員接報到場，證實男子已告氣絕身亡。警方在現場發現一條已截斷的繩子，且男子口部及鼻部流血受傷，不排除他在上吊不久後，尼龍繩截斷墜地，致失救死亡，正追查其身份。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180504/mobile/bkn-20180504091605093-0504_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180504%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180504091605093-0504_00822_001.html&d=r5NaYUvcD5nygBdEdwe5qjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=45ca9ac5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180504/mobile/bkn-20180504091605093-0504_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"45ffbd6a76721625acd34a8c45a588324b4b0ba4","tid":652552,"uid":148816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T05:05:58.000Z","msg":"死到咪得囉"},{"pid":"be25ece2c7f0a8123cbe2bc19d100e8a80897fe3","tid":652552,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T05:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}